sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant SYS as OCED Tracker
    participant MKT as Market Data
    participant CALC as P/L Engine
    participant OUT as Alerts/summary.md

    Note over SYS,OUT: Trigger logic (same for all tickers)
    SYS->>MKT: Pull S, C_close, delta (if available), DTE
    MKT-->>SYS: snapshot
    SYS->>CALC: Compute Δ = manual_PL - assignment_PL
    CALC-->>SYS: Δ, near_strike, rapid_up, wide_spread, low_liquidity

    alt Trigger = near_strike (|S-K|/K < 3%)
        SYS->>OUT: Escalate monitor cadence (hourly)
    else Trigger = rapid_up (1D return > +5%)
        SYS->>OUT: Escalate monitor cadence (hourly) + show "close/roll" delta
    else Trigger = delta meaningful (Δ > $75)
        SYS->>OUT: Alert "manual action justified"
    else Trigger = liquidity risk (spread% > 8% or health < 0.35)
        SYS->>OUT: Alert "execution risk" (prefer assignment or limit orders)
    else No triggers
        SYS->>OUT: Keep daily cadence only
    end
